image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, detailing ownership interests in various LLCs for Donald J. Trump. The document lists several entities, their owners, ownership percentages, and roles. It also includes a note about how real estate license fees are paid.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with form information and the filer's name. The main body is structured in a list format, with each entry representing an entity and its ownership details. A footer contains a general note, and a document identifier is at the very bottom.
